<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta name="layout" content="main"/>
    <title>MyadVenture</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="jumbotron masthead">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <center><h1><font color="#0332dd">Welcome to MyadVenture!</font></h1></center><br/>
        <p>Create your own venture and share ideas with others. You can specify the skillsets you need for your venture, and you can also search other users who have similar interests.</p><br/>
      </div>
      <div class="row-fluid">
        <ul class="thumbnails">
          <li class="span4">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="${resource(dir: 'images', file: 'ventures.png')}" alt="Create Ventures">
            </div>
          <center><h2> Create Ventures </h2></center>
          Create a venture for things you're interested in. Look for others who have special skills and specializations.
          </li>
          <li class="span4">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="${resource(dir: 'images', file: 'people.png')}" alt="Meet People">
            </div>
          <center><h2> Meet People </h2></center>
          Meet others who have similar interests.
          </li>
          <li class="span4">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <img src="${resource(dir: 'images', file: 'ideas.png')}" alt="Share Ideas">
            </div>
          <center><h2> Share Ideas </h2></center>
          Share your ideas with others, or find others with similar ideas!
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
